        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your eyes glow like bioluminescent lamps, and you have learned how to focus them into a directional beam. Your eyes shed light in a 30 foot line in any direction you're looking.</p>\n<p>You can suppress or restore this light as a free action. In addition, while this light is active you can take the Point Out action to indicate a creature within the area of your bioluminescence without making any noise, in which case it loses the auditory and manipulate traits. Finally, after you use an action to Hide or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Sneak], you can send predetermined signals with your lights to alert all allies you can see to your location as a free action.</p>"
